data.description: LOW FHA ASSUMABLE INTEREST RATE AVAILABLE- ask your agent for more info! Welcome to this delightful 1950's bungalow, located in the heart of Michigan City! Boasting 2 generously sized bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this home is perfect for those seeking to downsize or purchase their first home. This home features beautiful hardwood floors throughout, a spacious living room with large newer windows that provide an abundance of natural light, and a fully enclosed basement with plenty of room for storage. Outside you will find an oversized 1 car garage, side drive for additional parking as well parking behind the garage from the alleyway, and a fully fenced in yard. Schedule your showing for 213 Greenwood today!
